headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Interactive Brokers After Its Huge Multi Year Share Price Surge
summary: Wondering if Interactive Brokers Group is still a smart buy after such a big run, or if the value has already been priced in, you are not alone. The stock has pulled back about 6.3% over the last week and is down 1.5% over the past month, but it is still up 36.9% year to date and 44.5% over the last year, with 3 year and 5 year gains of 252.0% and 322.1% respectively.
